### Wishlist API Testing
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/customer/wishlist

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@access_token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Wishlist (Lấy danh sách wishlist của user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customer/wishlist
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### 2. Add to Wishlist (Toggle - Thêm hoặc xóa sản phẩm)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customer/wishlist
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}

###

### 3. Remove from Wishlist (Xóa sản phẩm khỏi wishlist)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customer/wishlist/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###
